{"title":"双色立交桥（二首）","authors":["于力"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":4,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"双色立交桥（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摩天楼摩天楼南方的男子汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥手，把空间变成了土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举足，把土地变成了空间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卡拉OK"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改变了这个纬度的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间变更线："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舞步把子夜拉回到白昼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生意在劲歌中缓缓洽谈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳和月亮拥抱在一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正如几个大洲相拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着魔幻彩灯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玻璃墙把记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染成蔚蓝："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广告——色彩是凝固的音响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车流——音响是流动的色斑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音与色的边界在这里打乱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摩天楼群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方的男子汉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正崛起在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄金海岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音乐喷泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水，站起来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袒露出动人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曲线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对微笑回以天使般的微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对热恋报以少女般的热恋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对冷静答以哲人般的冷静"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对果敢投以猎手般的果敢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国的水正如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国的风沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西部的高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都那么神奇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又那么简单"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南方每颗心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是一树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"音乐喷泉"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}